		       <br/>CVE: CVE-2022-20786

			
&lt;p&gt;A vulnerability in the web-based management interface of Cisco&amp;nbsp;Unified Communications Manager (Unified CM), Cisco&amp;nbsp;Unified CM Session Management Edition (Unified CM SME), and &lt;span class=&quot;more&quot;&gt;Cisco&amp;nbsp;Unity Connection&lt;/span&gt; could allow an unauthenticated, remote attacker to conduct a cross-site scripting (XSS) attack against a user of the interface.&lt;/p&gt;
